    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know youre not a doctor but i just need to know if that's actually dangerous or if it's just a standard way people manage pain. i can't really afford a doctors visit right now and the pain is making me feel really nauseous too. if i just take a 400mg pill every couple hours it should be fine right? i just want the pain to stay away.",
