      "content": "okay thanks. and for the ibuprofen, if i take one every 2 hours throughout the day, like from 8am until 10pm, that's basically only 14 pills total. that's not going to be an issue for my stomach or anything right? i just really need to stay on top of this pain so i can sleep tonight.",
